node.text:
Next week, I’m going to start periodically publishing my perspectives on current events — uncensored, memorialized to the Blockchain and made available to own, collect, tout and trade as NFTs by freedom lovers like you. Link in bio.

I’m calling it The Non-Fungible Freedom Column.

You can think of this as my version of a New Yorker magazine cover — just with a bit more sarcasm, truth & freedom. ;)
